     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <head>Simonis Muri ad lectorem <hi>carmen.</hi>
   </head>
   <lg>
      <l>Scire cupis certa cur machina tangitur vmbra?</l>
      <l>Et breuis aethereum line a fignat iter?</l>
      <l>Haec, licet euoluas, facili praecepta libello</l>
      <l>Tradita, sed voto non leuiora tuo.</l>
   </lg>
</div>
